{"tid":26802,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊記］我在雲南的17天","createTime":"2016-12-07T02:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T17:13:45.000Z","uid":22449,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e813ee07d10619390b56409598610fe811e68206","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"我既第一次遊記 若有不足 多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個人，一個背包，一次心血來潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就是一次旅程<br />\n<br />\n血液上腦就即plan行程，愈plan就覺得鬼國仙境名不虛傳，今次旅程總共17日，會係雲南昆明長水機場落機，終點係香格里拉普措達國家公園，途中會留昆明，大理，麗江先去香格里拉。<br />\n<br />\n主要係想放下假休息一下，洗滌心靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事不宜遲，即刻去馬！<br />\n<br />\n寫這篇遊記既時候已經係第二日早上，講一講第一日既驚險同遭遇先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/691Ge52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F691Ge52.jpg&h=623934b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/105207_539bd23f6360a5f50437f3fbcc6db1f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F105207_539bd23f6360a5f50437f3fbcc6db1f4.jpg&h=9a95c637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相中人不是我</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上緊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3aeacbd05996bb544f39e8b7fda846f08f5e12","tid":26802,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ced0cf75ac546e9acd347a09954dd957a9366a33","tid":26802,"uid":55273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n係另一個雲南post都有留<br />\n黎緊2月去8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002bcb882618a27800e9c82eae6aee660dd72d55","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"時間： 6-12-2016 黃昏<br />\n<br />\n上機後，望一望天氣報告，昆明當地氣溫為攝氏六度。我當堂眼中一閃，比起香港既2日冬天3日夏天既玩法，6度既氣溫先叫做有冬天既氣息！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係機上面不知不覺就訓左，正當我以為可以有一次唔錯既旅程之時，大媽們開始對我發動不死不休既攻勢，試圖將屬於我既周公殺死。既有不斷咳，咳足2個幾鐘既大媽，又有買免稅商店走去講價既大媽，仲有幾個帶左成間炸雞店上機食既大媽大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候講一講一些中國特色既畫面。<br />\n落機前不斷廣播入境要噴消毒噴霧，又要寫防疫表之類，播下播下唔知邊個熄左個廣播，無錯，係未播完架！<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐就落機，氣溫的確比香港涼爽，當時我只穿一年裇衫，暫時未感到有6度既寒冷。<br />\n準備入境，機場內人煙稀少，連機場地勤都唔見左，我發揮我既小宇宙，前面唔通有喪屍全部死曬？<br />\n行到防疫站，打開左既電腦屏幕，亮起紅燈既紅外線溫度計，但空空如也的座位似是在告訴我中國人民的團結？<br />\n再前行一點，檢查行李的檢查器，無錯！都係冇人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又再再前行，有一間小房間，嗯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都在蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離開機場，用50元搭的士去大板橋區搵間酒店休息，司機仲玩埋拼車，但價錢係無平過架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔理啦 帶住疲憊的身體求其搵間酒店休息<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/115136_0fc12caad6f8afd781f88f6134f74bac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F115136_0fc12caad6f8afd781f88f6134f74bac.jpg&h=819c0145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即刻去搵野食！<br />\n<br />\n見到街邊有燒烤店，即刻上！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/115329_a5a52c4c8ec186f41ec81c0598e923c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F115329_a5a52c4c8ec186f41ec81c0598e923c9.jpg&h=dbfe810f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫左8串正常既，點解係正常？<br />\n因為<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxKKLeY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxKKLeY.jpg&h=30da78a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有蟲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rw42evF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRw42evF.jpg&h=68f08093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20蚊食左8串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587d7cea9138b5bd8c72592c277334923ce7e243","tid":26802,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949920f55819ed6e1b8f8e12ed47d9e344a9c80e","tid":26802,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"去過雲南做義工，真係好正風景靚，野食又平，好想再去，不過咩7都加辣，就咁炒碟菜都加d辣椒先甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6f03595a5baabd4db668084266002ee8e10c40","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過雲南做義工，真係好正風景靚，野食又平，好想再去，不過咩7都加辣，就咁炒碟菜都加d辣椒先甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯！我叫佢啲串燒唔好加辣好似殺佢父母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bf8723963e8d26b0c2455ae6b23a7cd5f19806","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"講返小小行程既準備先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次旅程唔計機票<br />\n一共準備左CNY 10000左右<br />\n預計係唔會洗得曬既，帶多以防突發<br />\n<br />\n行程計劃方面主要係用螞蜂窩同ctrip<br />\n搭車就完全係亂黎，會用百度地圖，高德地圖，Google maps。亦會在青旅拼下車咁樣<br />\n<br />\n住宿就主要係青旅，如果無就會去酒店<br />\n 貴重野基本上唔帶<br />\n<br />\n手機同錢就係最貴果2樣<br />\n<br />\n諗到再補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa5097ca26a70c276a5d8bb800562f5ea328222","tid":26802,"uid":45728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:43:40.000Z","msg":"鬼國旅行 住宿點準備？你係去到見到邊間就住邊？"},{"pid":"56c698c0690fdff1ae835ef01115e0d459b54b24","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼國旅行 住宿點準備？你係去到見到邊間就住邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到邊住到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80effac92b2cabf41dc387a0e12ad52cf08fec98","tid":26802,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"雲南的確幾好 天氣舒服景靚 但好易中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去鬼國旅行想開心啲真係要隨遇而安<br />\n利申只係去過麗江 香格里拉 同西雙版納"},{"pid":"fd878101397a58d97bd83d5f1711ef1c90f09637","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲南的確幾好 天氣舒服景靚 但好易中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去鬼國旅行想開心啲真係要隨遇而安<br />\n利申只係去過麗江 香格里拉 同西雙版納</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9de8d13f93a800c8cc00e74d196e51d7505cde","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"時間：7-12-2016 早午<br />\n<br />\n原本既計劃係由大板橋出發去九鄉融洞，但由於搵唔到車既關係，故此押後一日join local去算。<br />\n<br />\n今日的景點係翠湖公園👉🏻雲南大學👉🏻金馬碧雞坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青旅正正坐落於翠湖公園隔離，2分鐘左右既路程就去到公園東門<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/143807_7e48c7260b99a6c29716a7443391f10f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F143807_7e48c7260b99a6c29716a7443391f10f.jpg&h=883ae241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面真心好多紅嘴鷗<br />\n完全唔怕人 有野食就湧過來搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/144019_796387d858d647428c339b7631a77342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F144019_796387d858d647428c339b7631a77342.jpg&h=fb780032&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OsU393F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOsU393F.jpg&h=3c55791b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面環境比想像中好，竹林荷塘，鴛鴦天鵝都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/144114_69ed30425301d06fd0b54fd7bbd0f5f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F144114_69ed30425301d06fd0b54fd7bbd0f5f0.jpg&h=2c2b3d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/144254_810e174e1f550c7b8e12e8a7dc3090f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F144254_810e174e1f550c7b8e12e8a7dc3090f2.jpg&h=e3c9489c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/144256_113591ee89bd6fe138cdde3c3e3f9b91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F144256_113591ee89bd6fe138cdde3c3e3f9b91.jpg&h=8dfde51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面仲有好多檔一模一樣既攤檔，應該係官方既鋪，間間都賣雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行左2個鐘 返一返青旅抖抖，下一站雲南大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f646537815088afffbf774b1e11ff8478c10b874","tid":26802,"uid":30962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bb024a7232c23557eecb37d2a4d5c64f567c67","tid":26802,"uid":52410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"上個月去完<br />\nplan黎緊4月再去<br />\n好鍾意麗江同香格里拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496ec586c60b2a9ba0155b3bab2975bdae45424d","tid":26802,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間： 6-12-2016 黃昏<br />\n<br />\n上機後，望一望天氣報告，昆明當地氣溫為攝氏六度。我當堂眼中一閃，比起香港既2日冬天3日夏天既玩法，6度既氣溫先叫做有冬天既氣息！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係機上面不知不覺就訓左，正當我以為可以有一次唔錯既旅程之時，大媽們開始對我發動不死不休既攻勢，試圖將屬於我既周公殺死。既有不斷咳，咳足2個幾鐘既大媽，又有買免稅商店走去講價既大媽，仲有幾個帶左成間炸雞店上機食既大媽大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候講一講一些中國特色既畫面。<br />\n落機前不斷廣播入境要噴消毒噴霧，又要寫防疫表之類，播下播下唔知邊個熄左個廣播，無錯，係未播完架！<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐就落機，氣溫的確比香港涼爽，當時我只穿一年裇衫，暫時未感到有6度既寒冷。<br />\n準備入境，機場內人煙稀少，連機場地勤都唔見左，我發揮我既小宇宙，前面唔通有喪屍全部死曬？<br />\n行到防疫站，打開左既電腦屏幕，亮起紅燈既紅外線溫度計，但空空如也的座位似是在告訴我中國人民的團結？<br />\n再前行一點，檢查行李的檢查器，無錯！都係冇人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又再再前行，有一間小房間，嗯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都在蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離開機場，用50元搭的士去大板橋區搵間酒店休息，司機仲玩埋拼車，但價錢係無平過架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔理啦 帶住疲憊的身體求其搵間酒店休息<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/115136_0fc12caad6f8afd781f88f6134f74bac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F115136_0fc12caad6f8afd781f88f6134f74bac.jpg&h=819c0145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即刻去搵野食！<br />\n<br />\n見到街邊有燒烤店，即刻上！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/115329_a5a52c4c8ec186f41ec81c0598e923c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F115329_a5a52c4c8ec186f41ec81c0598e923c9.jpg&h=dbfe810f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫左8串正常既，點解係正常？<br />\n因為<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxKKLeY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxKKLeY.jpg&h=30da78a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有蟲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rw42evF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRw42evF.jpg&h=68f08093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20蚊食左8串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為正常姐其實全部係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓肉來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0752548123286f1e5bdf84a99e12abfb9facc54e","tid":26802,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"lm 想5月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855eb3b1d0ffb3d1ee747bae2ce581639a6c77ba","tid":26802,"uid":25570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"月尾單機去留名<br />\n唔知巴打可唔可以share行程?<br />\n臨急臨忙決定去"},{"pid":"a5e261075f15b61ae43f37d7101b3baf6a63542a","tid":26802,"uid":9274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"我都諗住下年3-4月去"},{"pid":"2259733b71b88f1a5951aa571d3cde4ee71096c8","tid":26802,"uid":54291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"月尾去留名"},{"pid":"ae6474ea1186bfa10b0306e31a6f2c65b1f257ac","tid":26802,"uid":58608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"05598332dd57115990ff6ebbe66354c29e49f8a6","tid":26802,"uid":58608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n下年3月去。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 原來早去晚返比express 改到晚去早返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4058f3749264c52e09b61499af2675113685d63d","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間： 6-12-2016 黃昏<br />\n<br />\n上機後，望一望天氣報告，昆明當地氣溫為攝氏六度。我當堂眼中一閃，比起香港既2日冬天3日夏天既玩法，6度既氣溫先叫做有冬天既氣息！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係機上面不知不覺就訓左，正當我以為可以有一次唔錯既旅程之時，大媽們開始對我發動不死不休既攻勢，試圖將屬於我既周公殺死。既有不斷咳，咳足2個幾鐘既大媽，又有買免稅商店走去講價既大媽，仲有幾個帶左成間炸雞店上機食既大媽大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候講一講一些中國特色既畫面。<br />\n落機前不斷廣播入境要噴消毒噴霧，又要寫防疫表之類，播下播下唔知邊個熄左個廣播，無錯，係未播完架！<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐就落機，氣溫的