r />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓肉來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有咁多貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3861048a37cc419f0fb811846d3086d48563051","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月尾單機去留名<br />\n唔知巴打可唔可以share行程?<br />\n臨急臨忙決定去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0mot0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0mot0W.jpg&h=8d121431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概係咁 到時隨機應變"},{"pid":"a0f13829ce3d4e48f218585708e53c41b10acada","tid":26802,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n下年3月去。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 原來早去晚返比express 改到晚去早返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n差好遠喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}